WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Alice: Thanks everyone. We need to settle the beta launch plan for the analytics dashboard.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:16.500
Bob: QA cleared the internal build, but the external onboarding flow still needs one regression fix.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Priya: The final decision is to launch the beta to internal users first and delay public rollout by one week.

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:34.000
Alice: Bob, you will coordinate the regression fix by Thursday and share the release note draft.

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:43.000
Bob: I will send the updated checklist by Thursday afternoon.

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:52.000
Priya: We will go with a guided onboarding walkthrough for the first internal release.
